other_tests.findings: Detected two variants in the CYP19A1 gene; a novel single nucleotide deletion (c.570delT) and a novel missense mutation (c344G>A), with one variant classified as likely pathogenic and the other as of uncertain significance.

other_tests.procedure_name: Bone mineral density (BMD) determined by DXA scan
other_tests.findings: Z score of -2.5 at neck femur and -2.6 at lumbar spine; corresponding T-scores were -2.5 and -2.6, respectively.
